===============
didwegivecredit
===============


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/didwegivecredit.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/didwegivecredit

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/adswa/didwegivecredit.svg
